{
  "text": "and R has support on Z. To be precise, one introduces a superstructure on E \u2295 T * \u2126 so that U , f and \u2207 f are odd mappings whereas R is even; for details see [CITATION_1] Section 2] . However, for the purpose of this paper, the precise signs are not essential.",
  "correct_citation": {
